com.revolsys.jts.testold.generator

Class GridGenerator

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.revolsys.jts.testold.generator.GeometryGenerator
      • com.revolsys.jts.testold.generator.GridGenerator

  • public class GridGenerator
extends GeometryGenerator
    This class should be used to generate a grid of bounding boxes, most useful when creating multiple geometries. Successive calls to create() will walk the user though the grid. Use canCreate() and reset() to control the walk through the grid.
    Author:
    David Zwiers, Vivid Solutions.
    See Also:
    canCreate(), reset()
